7f65ef","tid":829203,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f5aa269ad43120d2b742f6f50487e14454a180","tid":829203,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bca1b5e56be1bfc1f1fe5f2937dabf096de19b6c","tid":829203,"uid":42921,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:04:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「如果你有廠在中國，你不會認命地選擇關門大吉，大家會想盡辦法提出更好的條件，」馮裕鈞說，「我不認為中國的產能會急遽下降。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中左傳銷毒咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"關稅每年25%， 人工又不斷上升，又有好多19環保政策，仲要唔確定中美打幾耐，不過唔會甘心離開中國？好難明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d2ad9bba6f3d123f67cdcafdb4858906900fd1","tid":829203,"uid":112583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 我又要出動<br />\n<br />\n貿易戰開始至今<br />\n中國己經大規模展開反擊措施<br />\n<br />\n加徵個人入息稅 + 全球徵稅<br />\n加徵遊戲稅35%<br />\n加徵演員稅6%&gt;&gt;&gt;45%<br />\n加徵骨灰保證金3000蚊<br />\n加徵電子商務法10%稅+17%增值稅"},{"pid":"0804687ef5baf4fae9222f0b23d32fe9db5e81d2","tid":829203,"uid":102179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國製造2025<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{